03:56.890 --> 03:58.920
Okay,i'm in...

04:00.250 --> 04:03.880
I joined,right after all of
that,alcoholics anonymous,

04:03.890 --> 04:05.050
And i am taking care of it,

04:05.060 --> 04:07.970
So i don't look at the drinking
thing as an active issue.

04:07.980 --> 04:10.630
How can it not be an
issue? You lied to me.

04:10.640 --> 04:11.660
I lied?

04:11.670 --> 04:15.020
You told me that you were
allergic to alcohol,but the --

04:15.030 --> 04:17.970
I called it an allergy because
that is how i think of it.

04:17.980 --> 04:19.970
How could you not tell
me you were in A.A.?

04:19.980 --> 04:22.990
Do i have to look up the word
"anonymous" for you in the dictionary?

04:23.000 --> 04:24.120
I'm not your friend.

04:24.130 --> 04:25.610
I'm not your coworker.

04:25.620 --> 04:27.200
I'm your fiancee.

04:27.210 --> 04:28.780
And if i'm marrying an alcoholic,

04:28.790 --> 04:30.020
Then i have a right to know about it.

04:30.030 --> 04:32.460
If you were getting married?

04:34.750 --> 04:36.260
I want an explanation.

04:36.270 --> 04:38.760
