04:40.700 --> 04:42.810
What?What?

04:42.820 --> 04:43.990
I don't know.

04:44.840 --> 04:46.470
I don't know.

04:48.300 --> 04:49.660
This is bull...

04:49.670 --> 04:51.440
I looked everywhere for this guy,

04:51.450 --> 04:52.600
And he was nowhere to be found.

04:52.610 --> 04:54.150
He shouldn't be too
hard to locate anymore.

04:54.160 --> 04:56.230
He's sitting in one of
your interview rooms,

04:56.240 --> 04:59.550
Where i assume even you can find him.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.700
