06:01.340 --> 06:03.200
Fine.

06:08.650 --> 06:10.490
I'm telling you,chief,he's
the right guy.

06:10.500 --> 06:12.930
I don't care what this
topper barnes guy says.

06:12.940 --> 06:14.600
The jury will care,lieutenant.

06:14.610 --> 06:16.280
They will care very much.

06:16.290 --> 06:17.740
If we can prove

06:17.750 --> 06:20.570
That the defense purposely
held mr. Barnes back from us,

06:20.580 --> 06:21.950
Then maybe we can get a mistrial.

06:21.960 --> 06:22.800
Of course they held him back.

06:22.810 --> 06:23.900
Why else wouldn't they tell us

06:23.910 --> 06:26.390
That topper's real
first name was eugene?

06:27.440 --> 06:29.310
You know the movie?

06:31.300 --> 06:33.020
Lieutenant tao,what do you have for me?

06:33.270 --> 06:35.900
Mr. Eugene,a.k.a.
"topper," barnes' statement

06:35.910 --> 06:37.590
Matches up with what dr. Schafer claims.

06:37.600 --> 06:39.980
They were on a four-day sailing trip.

06:40.450 --> 06:41.760
Topper's
criminal file --

06:41.770 --> 06:44.300
A couple drug busts and an
inconclusive assault charge.

06:44.310 --> 06:46.520
I think that might help.

06:46.530 --> 06:47.630
Yes,it will.

06:47.640 --> 06:49.960
It will very much. Thank you.

06:51.230 --> 06:52.950
Buzz,can i have an earpiece,please?

06:52.960 --> 06:54.350
Yes,ma'am.

06:54.710 --> 06:57.840
Mr. Garnett wants to assist me.

06:59.760 --> 07:01.520
Thank you.

07:02.180 --> 07:04.280
Now,if there is something
that you'd like to know,

07:04.290 --> 07:07.560
Please relay your
question to me quietly.

07:08.390 --> 07:11.080
Thank you so much.

07:11.580 --> 07:13.230
Have a seat.

07:18.050 --> 07:19.690
Mr. Barnes.

07:20.730 --> 07:22.000
Hi.

07:24.950 --> 07:26.760
So,do i have to talk to you guys?

07:26.770 --> 07:29.250
Absolutely not,but
i'd really like to hear

07:29.260 --> 07:31.630
About your sailing
trip with dr. Schafer.

07:31.640 --> 07:33.130
Because there's nothing worse

07:33.140 --> 07:35.600
Than putting the wrong man on
trial,especially for murder,

07:35.610 --> 07:37.770
And around here,we like
to learn from our mistakes.

07:37.780 --> 07:38.390
Yeah?

07:38.400 --> 07:42.070
Well,you guys should be
geniuses,then,all the mistakes you make.

07:45.300 --> 07:47.930
So,i guess you'll hear what
i have to say on monday.

07:48.310 --> 07:49.890
It was nice meeting you.

07:51.260 --> 07:53.100
