07:53.110 --> 07:55.290
You have been under arrest four times

07:55.300 --> 07:57.620
For possession of a
controlled substance...

07:58.130 --> 08:01.880
And that you've been
convicted of drug dealing

08:01.890 --> 08:06.020
And that you have an outstanding
assault charge from two years ago.

08:06.030 --> 08:07.880
I did my time for the dealing,

08:07.890 --> 08:09.340
And that assault charge was dropped.

08:09.350 --> 08:10.570
No,it wasn't.

08:10.580 --> 08:15.980
The victim,a mr. Robert
grimes,refused to press charges.

08:15.990 --> 08:17.560
But mr. Grimes is in prison now.

08:17.570 --> 08:19.600
I bet if i offered to
make his life easier,

08:19.610 --> 08:21.560
He'd help me out by
reinstating the assault charge.

08:21.570 --> 08:23.310
And then you could sit here
and talk with me all night

08:23.320 --> 08:25.190
Because you'd be under arrest.

08:25.200 --> 08:27.810
Or you could sit right back down.

08:28.280 --> 08:29.550
I'm just gonna tell you the same thing

08:29.560 --> 08:31.860
I told jonathan's attorney,mr. Cordry.

08:31.870 --> 08:34.380
It turns out that's
exactly what i want to hear.

08:37.270 --> 08:38.860
Well,all right,darlin'.

08:38.870 --> 08:40.070
What do you want to know?

08:41.750 --> 08:43.510
Where's he been?

08:43.940 --> 08:47.060
Chief,mr. Garnett wants you to
ask mr. Barnes where he's been.

08:47.070 --> 08:48.850
I guess my first question is,

08:48.860 --> 08:53.320
Were you aware that you were withholding
valuable information from a murder trial?

08:53.330 --> 08:54.700
I didn't even know there was a trial.

08:54.710 --> 08:55.870
I was out of the country.

08:55.880 --> 08:57.480
Where?

08:57.490 --> 08:59.050
Really? Where?

08:59.540 --> 09:02.360
Mexico. I got a place,about
50 miles north of cabo.

09:02.370 --> 09:04.590
I spend most of my time down there.

09:04.600 --> 09:06.820
Doing what,exactly? I have a boat.

09:06.830 --> 09:09.570
Yes,we've heard about your
boat -- the super plum.

09:10.590 --> 09:11.870
The sugar plum.

09:11.880 --> 09:13.870
See,that's another mistake we made.

09:13.880 --> 09:16.150
Dr. Schafer must have
gotten the name wrong.

09:16.160 --> 09:18.530
He should take a look at his eye chart.

09:18.540 --> 09:20.020
Would you please just tell her to ask

09:20.030 --> 09:22.220
Why the hell he just
happened to be in town?

09:22.630 --> 09:24.590
Mr. Garnett wants you to ask mr. Barnes

09:24.600 --> 09:27.210
Why the hell he just
happened to be in town.

09:27.220 --> 09:28.750
Sorry.

09:30.440 --> 09:32.050
What's she doing?

09:32.330 --> 09:34.080
What are you doing?

09:34.380 --> 09:36.700
So,tell me,mr. Barnes,

09:36.710 --> 09:39.880
What do you do 50 miles north of cabo?

09:40.290 --> 09:42.490
You know,i got a
little charter business.

09:42.500 --> 09:43.890
I take tourists out fishing.

09:43.900 --> 09:46.780
I don't need much. The drinks are cheap.

09:46.790 --> 09:48.590
And so are the women.

09:49.000 --> 09:50.660
And how do you know dr. Schafer?

09:50.670 --> 09:52.990
From college. We were
in the same fraternity.

09:53.000 --> 09:54.670
So you two were close.

09:54.680 --> 09:55.620
Yeah,we stayed friends,

09:55.630 --> 09:57.100
And every time i come up the coast,

09:57.110 --> 09:58.610
I stop here,i give him a call,

09:58.620 --> 10:01.900
See if he's too successful
to come play with me.

10:01.910 --> 10:03.420
That's what you did the
last time you were in town --

10:03.430 --> 10:05.460
You called him up and
invited him on your boat?

10:05.470 --> 10:08.360
Yeah,we went down to
ensenada for a few days.

10:08.670 --> 10:11.250
Fishing,drinking beer,the usual stuff.

10:11.260 --> 10:12.920
I'm unfamiliar with the usual stuff.

10:12.930 --> 10:14.650
Could you describe it?

10:15.900 --> 10:18.200
You know what? It's your lucky day.

10:18.210 --> 10:20.850
I have video.

10:21.550 --> 10:23.930
That's our trip to ensenada right there.

10:26.370 --> 10:28.210
Next best thing to being there.

10:28.220 --> 10:29.970
Knock yourself out.

10:33.370 --> 10:34.740
***he's still taking line.

10:34.750 --> 10:37.000
I can't put any more drag on him.

10:37.010 --> 10:38.580
Gonna break the line with any more drag.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.820
You go in there to
break schafer's alibi,

10:41.830 --> 10:43.710
