10:44.740 --> 10:46.250
The real deal. I told you,pal.

10:46.260 --> 10:47.800
I told you.

10:47.810 --> 10:49.670
Chief johnson,i think we
need to accept the fact

10:49.680 --> 10:51.970
That dr. Schafer may be innocent.

10:51.980 --> 10:53.420
I don't.

10:53.880 --> 10:55.160
Lieutenant flynn and provenza,

10:55.170 --> 10:57.570
Follow up,please,on mr. Barnes.

10:57.580 --> 11:00.480
Make sure he really has been
out of the country all this time.

11:00.490 --> 11:02.070
Lieutenant tao and buzz,

11:02.080 --> 11:05.020
I need you to make sure
that this video is genuine.

11:05.030 --> 11:07.810
And detective sanchez,check
out those boats,please.

11:07.820 --> 11:11.030
Find out who --
wait a minute.

11:11.040 --> 11:12.660
What is it,chief?

11:20.110 --> 11:21.770
Who was holding the camera?

11:22.170 --> 11:23.620
Someone was videotaping you.

11:23.630 --> 11:25.730
Oh,um...

11:26.320 --> 11:27.840
You know,when i go out,

11:27.850 --> 11:29.680
I just hire these local
guys right off the dock.

11:29.690 --> 11:30.520
There's a million of them.

11:30.530 --> 11:33.070
This kid's name -- i
don't know -- carlos?

11:33.080 --> 11:35.200
I'd never seen him
before. I paid him cash.

11:35.210 --> 11:37.760
As soon as we docked,he took off.*****

11:37.770 --> 11:39.600
Why didn't dr. Schafer
tell us about carlos?

11:39.610 --> 11:42.170
Two alibi witnesses are better than one.

11:43.150 --> 11:45.200
I don't know. Maybe he
didn't remember his name.

11:45.210 --> 11:47.330
Where is carlos now?

11:47.340 --> 11:48.070
I don't know.

11:48.080 --> 11:51.030
I told you,he took off
as soon as we docked.

11:51.040 --> 11:52.910
You want to go down to cabo?
I'll sail you down there.

11:52.920 --> 11:56.050
We'll go on a carlos
hunt,just you and me.

11:56.060 --> 11:57.640
It could be fun.

12:09.470 --> 12:11.650
You don't even want to say hello.

12:17.440 --> 12:18.720
Hello.

12:18.960 --> 12:20.750
I'm tired,and i have to
go straight back to work,

12:20.760 --> 12:22.580
So now is not a good time.

12:26.540 --> 12:27.910
It's all right...

12:28.370 --> 12:30.200
Because i don't have a lot to say.

12:34.660 --> 12:37.730
I got both the d.u.i.s
you were asking about

12:37.740 --> 12:40.320
In my own car,off the clock.

12:40.330 --> 12:42.030
And after the second one,i
went directly to my office,

12:42.040 --> 12:44.820
I reported what happened
and put myself in rehab,

12:44.830 --> 12:46.940
Which saved my job.

12:46.950 --> 12:49.510
Maybe my life,too.

12:49.520 --> 12:51.470
Is that why elaine divorced you?

12:51.480 --> 12:53.190
The drinking?

12:53.530 --> 12:55.580
Her name is cindy.

12:56.170 --> 12:58.700
My ex-wife's name is cindy. Okay?

12:58.710 --> 13:00.620
I don't even know anyone named elaine.

13:00.630 --> 13:01.770
And cindy is another story.

