And the location where
they are in the --

15:20.180 --> 15:20.720
Sorry.

15:20.980 --> 15:22.770
The location where they are in this shot

15:22.780 --> 15:24.660
Is just off the coast
of ensenada,mexico,

15:24.670 --> 15:26.740
Between the hours of 2:00 and 4:00 p.m.,

15:26.750 --> 15:28.780
Pacific standard time,on
the day of the murder.

15:28.790 --> 15:30.350
How can you be so sure?

15:30.360 --> 15:33.040
Do you see that cruise ship
in the background,chief?

15:33.050 --> 15:34.650
That's the pacific western.

15:34.660 --> 15:36.340
It only docks in mexico twice a year.

15:36.350 --> 15:38.190
The fact that it is heading out to sea

15:38.200 --> 15:41.250
Verifies time,date,and location.

15:41.570 --> 15:44.050
It's almost as if dr. Schafer
knew he was gonna need an alibi

15:44.060 --> 15:45.990
When this video was taken.

15:46.000 --> 15:50.300
Oh,and i checked into mr.
Barnes' charter company.

15:50.970 --> 15:52.020
It's for real.

15:52.030 --> 15:54.890
Eugene's boat service,based
out of cabo san lucas,

15:54.900 --> 15:57.020
And it's seasonal,like he said.

15:57.830 --> 15:59.880
Detective daniels,what
do you have for me?

15:59.890 --> 16:01.180
The flarpl.

16:01.190 --> 16:03.260
They're usually issued
when there's a question

16:03.270 --> 16:04.610
Of how the attorney will be paid,

16:04.620 --> 16:07.440
And dr. Schafer is a highly
successful ophthalmologist.

16:07.450 --> 16:08.940
So why would his wife's attorney

16:08.950 --> 16:10.640
Need to put a lien on their house?

16:10.650 --> 16:11.310
I don't know.

16:11.320 --> 16:14.390
I can't explain where the
money from his practice goes.

16:14.400 --> 16:17.170
He doesn't seem to take anything
from his business,really.

16:17.180 --> 16:22.460
I,uh...i feel like i haven't
done my best on this case,

16:22.470 --> 16:24.420
And i don't know why.

16:24.600 --> 16:26.290
I'm sorry.

16:26.300 --> 16:29.600
That's okay.we all make mistakes.

16:30.260 --> 16:31.630
Maybe i...

16:32.260 --> 16:34.640
Maybe i made a really big one.

16:35.520 --> 16:38.060
In fact,the only person
i've run into all week

16:38.070 --> 16:41.250
Who seems to have a good explanation
for everything is dr. Schafer.

16:42.740 --> 16:44.270
All right,um...

16:44.800 --> 16:46.310
Detective daniels,valerie henry said

16:46.320 --> 16:48.690
That the victim's billing
information wasn't privileged,

16:48.700 --> 16:50.860
So see if you can
get ahold of that fl--

16:52.700 --> 16:55.150
Flarpl for me,please.

16:55.160 --> 16:58.210
It's a public document. I
can't get it until monday.

16:59.760 --> 17:02.570
Or mrs. Henry might be able to help us.

17:04.130 --> 17:06.550
I have the financial files.

17:06.560 --> 17:07.880
What would you like to know?

17:07.890 --> 17:10.550
Your husband asked for
and received a flarpl,

17:10.560 --> 17:12.530
But dr. Schafer's a wealthy man.

17:12.540 --> 17:13.520
The judge could have ordered him

17:13.530 --> 17:15.510
To write a check for
his wife's attorney fee.

17:15.520 --> 17:17.839
Yes,usually that's what
ollie would have recommended,

17:17.849 --> 17:19.960
But it turns out,not surprisingly,

17:19.970 --> 17:22.119
Since he was having an affair,

17:22.130 --> 17:24.790
That the schafers' bank
accounts were nearly empty.

17:24.800 --> 17:26.819
So,ollie did a little investigating,

17:26.829 --> 17:29.160
And he found out that the doctor had,

17:29.170 --> 17:34.140
A couple of years ago,put a
lot of money into a second home.

17:34.380 --> 17:36.470
- so,he put a lien on
that - -i-i'm sorry.

17:36.830 --> 17:38.140
A second home?

17:39.050 --> 17:40.890
In l.a.,too.

17:40.900 --> 17:44.950
Very close to his primary
residence.isn't that odd?

17:44.960 --> 17:47.090
And then when dr. Schafer
found out about the lien

17:47.100 --> 17:49.240
On that residence,he
hit the roof --

17:49.250 --> 17:50.490
Threatened ollie.

17:50.500 --> 17:52.700
And your ex-husband told you that?

17:52.710 --> 17:53.940
Oh,no,no.

17:53.950 --> 17:56.050
Ollie took privilege seriously.

17:56.060 --> 17:57.720
He didn't want me to
worry about threats.

17:57.730 --> 17:59.890
No,i was there.

17:59.900 --> 18:03.090
Dr. Schafer came into the office.

18:03.920 --> 18:05.690
And the only other thing i can tell you

18:05.700 --> 18:07.830
Is that mrs. Schafer asked ollie

18:07.840 --> 18:11.530
To take her to this
new house,and he did.

18:11.980 --> 18:13.430
But around that time,

18:13.440 --> 18:16.590
Ollie and i had an argument
about the dogs,and we...

18:19.010 --> 18:21.220
And we never spoke again.

18:22.760 --> 18:26.910
Looks like mrs. Schafer
paid us by a cashier's check

18:26.920 --> 18:31.320
Two days before ollie died
to get the flarpl removed.

18:31.330 --> 18:33.250
And he released the lien?

18:33.260 --> 18:37.050
Well,he probably would have
that monday,but he died...

18:37.420 --> 18:39.430
Or was murdered.

18:39.440 --> 18:41.780
And if he was,then it's my fault,

18:41.790 --> 18:44.150
Because if i hadn't filed
for divorce from ollie,

18:44.160 --> 18:46.410
He never would have been
alone in the house that night,

18:46.420 --> 18:49.180
And he never would have made
it to the bottom of that pool.

18:49.190 --> 18:51.720
And here i am,living with
everything we've ever owned,

18:51.730 --> 18:55.460
And it means nothing
because i don't have him.

18:57.880 --> 18:59.430
If i had
just --

19:00.970 --> 19:02.750
If i...

19:03.410 --> 19:09.430
"if"...is a...very
hard word to live with.

19:11.580 --> 19:13.070
But...

19:13.450 --> 19:15.400
You're living here again.

19:15.410 --> 19:18.230
Your ex-husband never changed his will.

19:18.240 --> 19:20.300
Yes,well...

19:21.630 --> 19:23.450
Yes,i guess...

19:24.190 --> 19:26.860
He was a bit neglectful
of his personal papers.

19:26.870 --> 19:30.520
Or maybe he wanted
you to have this place.

19:31.540 --> 19:33.340
That,in spite of everything...

19:34.550 --> 19:36.480
He still loved you.

19:37.960 --> 19:40.000
Maybe,i guess.

19:41.730 --> 19:43.450
All right.

19:45.640 --> 19:47.880
Dr. Schafer's other property,

19:48.330 --> 19:50.940
The one the flarpl was
issued against,is in westwood.

19:50.950 --> 19:53.470
How is it that we're just
hearing about this property now?

19:53.480 --> 19:57.260
I've been through the schafers'
finances and nothing like this came up.

20:00.980 --> 20:02.770
It wouldn't...

20:02.780 --> 20:05.060
Because it's not in the schafers' name.

20:05.070 --> 20:07.360
It's owned by jonathan
schafer's practice,

20:07.370 --> 20:09.950
Listed as a second clinic.

20:09.960 --> 20:12.550
But it's not in an
area zoned for business.

20:12.560 --> 20:14.000
And the address?

20:14.010 --> 20:17.300
2501 partridge drive.

21:06.710 --> 21:08.270
Lieutenant flynn.

21:08.950 --> 21:10.660
Fancy meeting you here.

21:10.670 --> 21:13.600
Chief,you have no idea.

21:24.110 --> 21:25.470
Chief.

21:25.480 --> 21:27.270
Every room in the house is like this.

21:27.280 --> 21:29.620
There must be close
to 4,000 plants here.

21:29.630 --> 21:31.130
I'm telling you,this much marijuana's

21:31.140 --> 21:32.690
Got to be worth $10 million,$12 million.

21:32.960 --> 21:36.390
And how did following up on
mr.Eugene barnes lead you here?

21:36.400 --> 21:41.800
Well,guess who gets his mail
delivered to 2501 partridge drive.

21:44.580 --> 21:46.670
Utility bills.

21:46.680 --> 21:50.420
Bet they use an awful lot of
electricity to run all of this equipment.

21:50.430 --> 21:55.590
And,gee,I wonder what mr.Barnes
uses his boat for in the off-season.

21:57.890 --> 21:59.940
Oh,for heaven sakes.

22:02.130 --> 22:03.780
Schafer,is your husband home?

22:03.950 --> 22:05.220
What is this about?

22:05.230 --> 22:06.900
I have a search warrant.

22:06.910 --> 22:08.060
What the hell is going on here?

22:08.070 --> 22:10.300
An arrest warrant for
you,sir.Jonathan schafer,

22:10.310 --> 22:13.590
you are under arrest for the cultivation
of and possession to sell marijuana.

22:13.600 --> 22:16.240
You have the right to
remain silent*******

22:16.250 --> 22:17.470
Jonathan,What is going on?

22:17.480 --> 22:19.130
Call cordry.Have him meet me downtown.

22:19.140 --> 22:19.890
Daddy!

22:19.900 --> 22:20.750
It's okay,honey.

22:20.760 --> 22:22.050
******

22:22.060 --> 22:24.040
- Did you understand****?
- Yes.

22:24.050 --> 22:26.070
Kristen,have cordry meet me!

22:26.080 --> 22:28.510
Honey,go to your room right now.

22:28.520 --> 22:30.280
Lieutenants flynn
and provenza --

22:30.290 --> 22:31.790
arrest mr.Topper barnes?

22:31.800 --> 22:32.980
If you would,please.

22:32.990 --> 22:34.810
Our pleasure,chief.

22:49.890 --> 22:50.740
No,thanks.

22:50.750 --> 22:52.570
sit down.sit down.Let's just sit down.

22:54.340 --> 22:56.780
The best thing to do
is not to say anything.

22:58.190 --> 23:01.250
Mr.Cordry,dr.Schafer,topper.

23:01.260 --> 23:04.090
Your actions today are those
of a desperate individual.

23:04.100 --> 23:06.180
First,you arrest the
wrong man for the murder,

23:06.190 --> 23:08.690
then you compound that error
by arresting topper barnes.

23:08.700 --> 23:11.420
Sir,are you aware that dr.Schafer here

23:11.430 --> 23:16.960
owns a house containing 4,000 marijuana
plants worth approximately $12 million?

23:16.970 --> 23:18.720
He's an agricultural tycoon.

23:21.140 --> 23:24.370
Schafer's going back to jail without
bond.He's gonna stay there,too.

23:24.380 --> 23:29.560
Let his jerk lawyer explain why his client is
entering the courtroom through the prison door.

23:29.570 --> 23:32.590
And your other
client,mr.Barnes,was his gardener.

23:32.600 --> 23:34.600
So it seems to me that you
have a very big problem --

23:34.610 --> 23:35.980
he's an ophthalmologist.

23:35.990 --> 23:38.340
Medical marijuana is
legal in california.

23:38.350 --> 23:40.880
They use it for glaucoma and cataracts.

23:40.890 --> 23:45.460
Well,judging by the amount of pot you have on
hand,sir,you must be bracing for an epidemic.

23:45.770 --> 23:47.410
Sergeant gabriel,let's
get garnett in here.

23:47.420 --> 23:48.890
I believe we have our motive.

23:48.900 --> 23:54.240
Dr.Schafer here may have set you up by having you
register the utilities at his house in your name.

23:54.250 --> 23:56.350
Maybe he'll claim you
were renting the place.

23:56.560 --> 23:59.460
Don't listen to her.Allow me
to excuse your ignorance,ma'am,

23:59.470 --> 24:02.220
by pointing out that medical
marijuana is available by prescrip--

24:02.230 --> 24:03.900
jonathan,let me handle this.

24:03.910 --> 24:08.340
Just because my client owns a house in which
marijuana was cultivated does not make him a killer.

24:08.350 --> 24:11.580
And none of this,by the way,is
admissible in the current trial.

24:11.590 --> 24:14.020
The fact that the victim put
a lien on your client's house,

24:14.030 --> 24:18.540
a house containing over $12 million in
marijuana,just might be of interest to the judge.

24:18.550 --> 24:19.930
Well,we'll see about that.

24:19.940 --> 24:21.500
Wait a second.

24:22.150 --> 24:24.320
- Take it back a few frames.
- Yeah,I saw it,too.

24:24.740 --> 24:26.020
Right about...

24:26.030 --> 24:28.040
stop.*******

24:28.050 --> 24:30.020
Let me enhance this.

24:33.420 --> 24:36.080
Doesn't look like a carlos to me.

24:36.090 --> 24:38.210
Who's that in the
reflection?Do we know her?

24:38.220 --> 24:41.430
Yeah.That's schafer's ex-girlfriend.

24:41.440 --> 24:44.250
Though I'm beginning to
doubt about how ex she is.

24:44.260 --> 24:47.430
A direct violation of
their constitutional rights.

24:50.080 --> 24:53.620
So,I'm not under arrest,or
-- or do I need a lawyer?

24:53.630 --> 24:57.040
No,you are not under arrest,and
you don't need a lawyer.

24:57.890 --> 25:00.940
Because,fortunately,for you,lying
to the police is not against the law.

25:00.950 --> 25:03.640
We just wanted to
straighten a few things out.

25:03.650 --> 25:07.650
Have you tell us the truth this
time,since we already know most of it.

25:09.650 --> 25:10.970
How about that?

25:10.980 --> 25:13.180
Have a seat,if you would,please.

25:13.620 --> 25:18.490
Well,but I -- I knew
jonathan was innocent.

25:19.140 --> 25:21.330
And he promised me...

25:21.890 --> 25:23.830
that you'd figure that out in the end.

25:23.840 --> 25:26.910
Then why not tell us that you were on the
boat with dr.Schafer from the very beginning?

25:26.920 --> 25:30.680
You could have been his alibi when
we couldn't find topper barnes.

25:30.690 --> 25:34.540
Jonathan asked me not to say anything
about being on the boat with him.

25:34.550 --> 25:36.730
He thought my getting wrapped
up in a murder investigation,

25:36.740 --> 25:39.800
that it would hurt my
career -- the scandal.

25:41.440 --> 25:45.220
We all know how horrible scandal
is for an aspiring actress' career.

25:45.560 --> 25:46.670
No.

25:46.910 --> 25:50.850
No,I don't think that jonathan schafer
was trying to protect you,michelle.

25:50.860 --> 25:51.880
At all.

25:51.890 --> 25:54.590
He was,though.He was.And he's innocent.

25:54.600 --> 25:56.870
He was with me when that
attorney was murdered.

25:56.880 --> 26:01.570
If you were on the boat,how come you're
not in the video,other than the reflection?

26:01.990 --> 26:05.780
Jonathan told me to just hold the
camera and not say anything,which was...

26:05.790 --> 26:09.340
fine with me -- anything to keep
the relationship going,I guess.

26:09.890 --> 26:13.380
I mean,the whole weekend
was a surprise,anyway.

26:13.390 --> 26:14.570
A surprise?

26:14.580 --> 26:15.420
Yeah.

26:15.430 --> 26:18.470
I found out that morning when
jonathan showed up at my apartment.

26:18.480 --> 26:21.940
He told me to pack,and
then we went to the marina.

26:24.240 --> 26:25.910
In your car?

26:25.920 --> 26:28.750
- No,jonathan took me - 
- are you sure?

26:29.170 --> 26:32.860
Jonathan picked you up
and took you to the marina?

26:34.210 --> 26:36.490
Uh-huh --
marina del rey.

26:37.850 --> 26:40.750
Okay.Thank you,michelle.

26:43.090 --> 26:44.380
Okay.

26:44.390 --> 26:47.130
Did I clear things up for you,then?

26:47.140 --> 26:49.310
Yes,you certainly did.

26:51.490 --> 26:53.440
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

27:03.290 --> 27:07.130
Chief,we received the security photos from
the marina parking lot,and we got a match.

27:07.140 --> 27:09.520
Lieutenant tao has them
in the electronics room.

27:09.940 --> 27:10.960
Thank you,detective.

27:11.430 --> 27:13.230
You're not trying to do anything!

27:13.240 --> 27:14.780
Ma'am,you need to calm down.

27:14.790 --> 27:16.140
Don't tell me to calm down!

27:16.150 --> 27:20.510
I have been sitting here for over
two hours waiting to talk to somebody!

27:20.520 --> 27:22.450
Well,I am just that
somebody.How can I help you?

27:22.460 --> 27:24.480
I went to post bail for my husband,

27:24.490 --> 27:28.430
and I was told that you and that horrible
district attorney requested no bond?

27:28.440 --> 27:31.690
That's true.I was hoping
I could explain things.

27:31.700 --> 27:34.710
The judge already decided that my
husband was not a flight risk,so --

27:34.720 --> 27:36.070
but that was for the murder.

27:36.080 --> 27:39.660
That was before the court knew about
the $12 million worth of marijuana

27:39.670 --> 27:41.780
grown at your husband's westwood house.

27:41.790 --> 27:44.320
Now his flight-risk status has changed.

27:44.330 --> 27:48.820
So,sergeant gabriel,would you please escort
mrs.Schafer to the electronics room?Thank you

27:48.830 --> 27:50.940
I'll be right there to
straighten things out.

27:50.950 --> 27:52.660
This way,please.

27:52.670 --> 27:54.660
Thank you.

27:58.630 --> 28:00.120
Mr.Garnett.

28:00.520 --> 28:01.480
Perfect timing.

28:01.490 --> 28:03.790
Deputy chief johnson,is it true?

28:03.800 --> 28:05.180
Is what true,sir?

28:05.190 --> 28:08.480
Did you place michelle edwards on the
same boat as dr.Schafer the weekend

28:08.490 --> 28:10.340
he's supposed to have murdered mr.Henry?

28:10.350 --> 28:12.170
Well,yes,it is.

28:12.180 --> 28:13.570
Congratulations.

28:13.580 --> 28:17.950
You've confirmed the alibi of the defendant,as well
as the two people most likely to have assisted him.

28:18.640 --> 28:22.470
Honestly,I've come to believe
this case should be dismissed

28:22.480 --> 28:23.850
because you arrested the wrong man.

28:23.860 --> 28:25.900
I have not arrested the wrong man.

28:25.910 --> 28:29.430
And before you dismiss the charges,you
might want to hear the confession.

28:29.440 --> 28:30.930
Besides,I need you to make a deal.

28:30.940 --> 28:32.900
A confession?

28:32.910 --> 28:33.980
Are you crazy?

28:33.990 --> 28:35.440
Cordry's never gonna
let schafer talk to you.

28:35.450 --> 28:38.080
Do you want to win your case or not?

28:39.250 --> 28:41.250
Come with me,sir.

28:44.430 --> 28:48.000
Mrs.Schafer,I'm so sorry
to keep you waiting.

28:48.010 --> 28:50.110
Would you like a tissue or something?

28:50.120 --> 28:53.390
No,I just -- I just
want my husband home.

28:53.400 --> 28:55.490
And I have to
-- I have to go.

28:55.500 --> 28:58.270
I couldn't find a sitter,and
my daughter,beverly,

28:58.280 --> 29:00.910
she's been home alone
for over two hours now.

29:00.920 --> 29:03.930
Well,let me relieve your
mind about one thing...

29:03.940 --> 29:06.830
because beverly's here with us.

29:09.650 --> 29:12.480
And we are keeping her very safe.

29:12.490 --> 29:14.610
What is beverly...

29:15.450 --> 29:17.630
what are you doing with my daughter?

29:17.640 --> 29:19.700
We're just asking her a few questions.

29:19.710 --> 29:23.810
Tell me,ma'am,do you ever
borrow your husband's car?

29:27.090 --> 29:28.600
- No.
- Really?

29:28.610 --> 29:31.990
Because beverly remembers
things differently.

29:32.010 --> 29:37.690
She says that jonathan drove your car to the
marina the weekend oliver henry was killed.

29:37.700 --> 29:42.380
These pictures were taken from a
parking-lot security camera in marina del rey

29:42.390 --> 29:45.180
two days before your
attorney was murdered.

29:48.700 --> 29:51.620
This is your car entering the lot,yes?

29:51.630 --> 29:54.310
The vanity plates say mrs.Eyes.

29:56.260 --> 30:01.570
Same security camera four days
later -- your car exiting the lot.

30:01.580 --> 30:04.590
And it clearly shows your
husband paying the cashier.

30:04.600 --> 30:09.190
So,if jonathan was driving your car,the
question is,which car were you driving?

30:10.140 --> 30:13.340
Or maybe it's like beverly says...

30:13.630 --> 30:16.180
mommy was driving daddy's car.

30:17.900 --> 30:20.200
What's -- what's
going on here?

30:24.420 --> 30:27.950
Mrs.Schafer filed for divorce
with a fine,upstanding attorney --

30:27.960 --> 30:31.060
a decent guy,a former eagle scout.

30:31.070 --> 30:35.090
And he went after her husband,trying to find
where he might have hidden his resources.

30:35.100 --> 30:36.600
And he discovered a second residence.

30:36.610 --> 30:40.790
And what did you
find,mrs.Schafer,at that second home?

30:41.420 --> 30:42.990
You know.

30:43.000 --> 30:45.390
I mean,you know already.

30:47.060 --> 30:51.730
I thought that we were doing so well
because jonathan was a great doctor.

30:52.440 --> 30:56.820
I had no idea that our money
was coming from selling drugs.

30:56.830 --> 30:59.060
And mr.Henry said,this is great.

30:59.070 --> 31:00.670
Your husband's involved
in a criminal enterprise.

31:00.680 --> 31:02.480
You're gonna get sole
custody of your daughter,

31:02.490 --> 31:06.480
and after the government confiscates his
property,you'll get everything that's left.

31:06.490 --> 31:10.960
But everything didn't turn out
to be so much,did it,mrs.Schafer?

31:10.970 --> 31:12.690
Oh,my god.They did it together.

31:12.700 --> 31:15.330
I -- just --
sergeant gabriel.

31:15.340 --> 31:17.480
Kristen schafer,you have
the right to remain silent.

31:17.490 --> 31:20.500
Anything you say can and will be
used against you in a court of law.

31:20.510 --> 31:22.130
You have the right to an attorney.

31:22.140 --> 31:25.950
If you cannot afford an attorney,one
will be appointed by the court.

31:28.280 --> 31:30.730
Mrs.Schafer,do you
understand your rights?

